AD_TAB.NAME: Budget Log
AD_TAB.WHERECLAUSE: sfb_budget_log.sfb_budget_area_id IN ( select sfb_budget_area_id from sfb_budget_user_area where ad_user_id = @#AD_User_ID@)
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.area IN (select area from sfb_budget_user_area as ua where ua.userContact.id = @#AD_User_ID@)

AD_TAB.NAME: Header
AD_TAB.WHERECLAUSE: sfb_budget_certificate.sfb_budget_area_id IN ( select sfb_budget_area_id from sfb_budget_user_area where ad_user_id = @#AD_User_ID@) and sfb_budget_certificate.type_of_certificate = 'AM'
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.area IN (select area from sfb_budget_user_area as ua where ua.userContact.id = @#AD_User_ID@) and e.typeOfCertificate = 'AM'

AD_TAB.NAME: Header
AD_TAB.HELP: This window allows to manage the G/L item payments made in a G/L Journal.

AD_TAB.NAME: Header
AD_TAB.WHERECLAUSE: sfb_budget_certificate.sfb_budget_area_id IN ( select sfb_budget_area_id from sfb_budget_user_area where ad_user_id = @#AD_User_ID@) and sfb_budget_certificate.type_of_certificate = 'D'
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.area IN (select area from sfb_budget_user_area as ua where ua.userContact.id = @#AD_User_ID@) and e.typeOfCertificate = 'D'

AD_TAB.NAME: Line
AD_TAB.WHERECLAUSE: sfb_budget_line.sfb_budget_area_id IN ( select sfb_budget_area_id from sfb_budget_user_area where ad_user_id = @#AD_User_ID@)
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.area IN (select area from sfb_budget_user_area as ua where ua.userContact.id = @#AD_User_ID@)

AD_TAB.WHERECLAUSE: SFB_Budget_Line.IsTBN='Y' AND (SELECT SFB_Budget_Version.Version_Status FROM SFB_Budget_Version WHERE SFB_Budget_Version.SFB_Budget_Version_ID=SFB_Budget_Line.SFB_Budget_Version_ID)='AP'
